title: War of the Roses: His Car Was Not at the Golf Course
description: Ava's boyfriend has been golfing a lot lately which she thinks is great, at least she did until she asked his brother about it who he said he was golfing with and his brother didn't know what she was talking about.  She checked up on him one day at the golf course he was supposed to be at and he wasn't there so now she wants to see if he's cheating.
